    "Details": "<color=#F79B26>The Nexus is a recon striker 'Mech initially based on the Jackrabbit, a light scout and combined-arms support 'Mech built for the Star League Defense Force.</color>\n\nAs a recon 'Mech intended to rarely engage an enemy in a pitched battle, the Nexus is armed with a Medium Laser backed up by two highly-accurate Medium Pulse Lasers. As a last resort, the Nexus can employ  its two Small Lasers, while an Anti-Missile System offers additional defense against missile attacks. The Nexus' true strength resides in his endo steel chassis and its two tons of ferro-fibrous armor, which both save weight without the vulnerability of an extralight engine.",
